extends baseEmail
block content
   p Hi #{firstName},
   p Welcome to Natours, we're glad to have you 🎉🙏
   p We're all a big familiy here, please verify your account first to continue!
   p <b>Token: </b> #{token}
   p Use the token in the following link to verify.
   table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
      tbody
         tr
         td(align='left')
            table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
               tbody
               tr
                  td
                     a.verify-btn(href=`${url}`, target='_blank', onclick="return false;") Verify Account
   p Hope you have a great experience with us.